data.text:
Yippee Ki-Yay

In an effort to please Salen, Andrews takes on a high-profile case and assigns Shaun and Allen to help perform a risky surgery to restore the voice of a famous pop star.

The Darryl Dawkins Dance

Beverly picks out Barry's date for the Sadie Hawkins dance, and her choice comes as a shock to everyone; at the same time, Adam loses his best friend after he and Pops get into a fight.

Muscles Mirsky

While Adam (Sean Giambrone) worries about sexual tension between him and his longtime friend Emmy (guest star Stephanie Katherine Grant), Erica (Hayley Orrantia) and Beverly (Wendi McLendon-Covey) square off over a lack of trust.

The Age of Darkness

When Erica's boyfriend breaks up with her, she gets overwhelmed with heartbreak and Murray steps in to try to help her. Meanwhile, Barry starts to get obsessed with a new arcade game.

DannyDonnieJoeyJonJordan

Beverly is ordered to clean out the garage by Murray, who wants everything gone except for one trunk that he's particularly sentimental about. Meanwhile, Adam and Barry discover Erica's old collection of New Kids on the Block memorabilia.
